  - m_Id: 187096342528
    m_Localized: '"Basic Controls


      - WASD To Move


      - E to Switch Weapons


      -
      R to Reload


      - F to Pickup Item


      - SPACE to toggle to WIDE view


      -
      LMB to shoot (when not commanding operators)

      `- RMB to shoot secondary
      (for dual-wielded weapons)"


      - RMB to shoot secondary (for dual-wielded
      weapons)'
